title: Default Values Not Displayed in Show Report Parameters Dialog
description: When accessing the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog, default values for parameters are not displayed as expected.
OB: Upon opening the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values for parameters are not visible.
EB: The expected behavior is that when the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog is opened, it should display the default values for each parameter.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Launch the application.
2. Navigate to the 'Reports' section.
3. Select a report that has parameters.
4. Click on 'Show Report Parameters' to open the dialog.
5. Observe that the default values for the parameters are not shown.
